'''Marta Grandi''' (3 July 1915, [[Bologna]] – Bologna, 6 October 2005, Bologna ) was an [[Italy|Italian]] [[entomologist]] who specialised in [[Ephemeroptera]].

==Publications==

*''Ephemeroidea''. ''Fauna d'Italia'' 3:1-472 (1960).

See [https://archive.is/20071213152127/http://www.famu.org/mayfly/mfbib_fg.php Bibliography of Ephemeroptera]

